snippet.title: Funko Fusion - Five Nights at Freddy's Gameplay Showcase
snippet.description:
Survive Five Nights At Freddy’s in Funko Fusion!

Play through a level inspired by the first FNAF game, and survive five nights to unlock Freddy Fazbear and Foxy the Pirate as playable characters.

Funko Fusion releases September 13 on Steam, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X|S. Wishlist us and preorder today!

Also coming to PlayStation 4 on November 15, and Nintendo Switch in December.
